{"tid":310203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「人間胸器」正妹食炸雞被起底，結果讓網民呼極品","createTime":"2017-07-05T15:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T15:27:40.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74127880c097c31e2e6f0f7dcd27c28cc3467910","tid":310203,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"有鄉民日前在PTT「表特板」上分享數張正妹美照，引起熱議。只見照片中一名長髮妹子側身站在嘉義某鹹酥雞攤子前面，前凸後翹的性感曲線，再加上極其雄偉的豪乳、白皙雪肌，讓網友狂讚不已，驚呼「極品天菜啊！」<br />\n<br />\n鹹酥雞攤驚見「人間胸器」鄉民狂讚：極品天菜<br />\n正妹照片曝光後，引起鄉民熱議。（圖/翻攝自PTT）<br />\n正妹照片曝光後，鄉民也紛紛好奇她是哪國妹子，「看起來不像台灣人～但是居然有看到嘉義鹹酥雞」、「有小港機場和嘉義，台灣人？」、「越南人」、「有一張疑似在大阪城，到底是哪裡人啊？」引發眾人熱烈討論，最後有鄉民陸續跳出來指認，說道「嘉義人呀！某家汽修廠的千金，快嫁人了～」、「認識本人，本人真的長這樣，很漂亮，身材也是很驚人！」、「是嘉義人沒錯，看臉書照片有身材有臉蛋&hellip;讚！」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170705005723-260808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20170705005723-260808&d=S%2FTL4xa%2Bh793bcPae0TTPzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=22aa463c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20170705005723-260808</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/232411_263f3f0a99726a4d27679500c2ede84f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F232411_263f3f0a99726a4d27679500c2ede84f.jpg&h=45b275d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/232411_a20a2c15c59832962f2d0a5254f82421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F232411_a20a2c15c59832962f2d0a5254f82421.jpg&h=eba29bce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/232412_a20a2c15c59832962f2d0a5254f82421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F232412_a20a2c15c59832962f2d0a5254f82421.jpg&h=08eb2c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/232412_235be15293f9dec7d7aa60efa3fc6ab6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F232412_235be15293f9dec7d7aa60efa3fc6ab6.jpg&h=804f7628&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a81bd2a042475805f8050263fa6dcb60acf9ffce","tid":310203,"uid":3535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"假。人間胸器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}